strings.Value: "Is it just me who can't fall asleep at night? I'm scared that some uninvited guests might show up..."
"Looks like tonight something might happen that will be worth writing about..."
"We should try to avoid unexpected engagements. Although sometimes they're unavoidable."
"I understand you! But don't let such thoughts keep you awake."
"He who fears nothing sleeps tight... and he who sleeps tight, is fearing nothing! Hah, did you hear? Write that down, what I just said. Before we forget!"
"I'm bored to death with crawling through bushes, gathering branches and fetching armfuls of leaves. If someone's interested â€” be my guest. But you can do it without me this time."
"If Linzee keeps talk-talking, we will miss the whole greatbeast!"
